《'''柏捷頓家族：名門韻事'''》（{{lang-en|''Bridgerton''}}）是一部[[美國|美國]]的時代愛情[[網絡劇|網絡劇]]，在[[Netflix|Netflix]]上播映。故事改編自作家[[茱莉亞·昆恩|茱莉亞·昆恩]]的[[攝政時代|攝政羅曼史]]小說作品。<ref>[https://edition.cnn.com/2021/02/06/entertainment/bridgerton-romance-novel-renaissance-trnd/index.html “ Netflix's 'Bridgerton' is leading a romance novel renaissance”] {{Wayback|url=https://edition.cnn.com/2021/02/06/entertainment/bridgerton-romance-novel-renaissance-trnd/index.html |date=20210217154120 }} CNN [06-02-2021]</ref>以同一歷史時代為背景，《柏捷頓家族：名門韻事》講述一群英國貴族在[[社交季節|社交季節]]期間的愛恨情仇。<ref>[https://www.npr.org/2020/12/28/949236178/bridgerton-is-a-delicious-raunchy-tale-of-1-very-hot-family {{Wayback|url=https://www.npr.org/2020/12/28/949236178/bridgerton-is-a-delicious-raunchy-tale-of-1-very-hot-family |date=20210331175419 }} “ 'Bridgerton' Is A Delicious, Raunchy Tale Of One Very Hot Family” NPR [28-12-2020]</ref>第一季於2020年12月25日播出；第二季則於2022年3月25日播出。<ref>{{cite web |title=Bridgerton Season 2 | Official Teaser | Netflix |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bs9r1UbmFAI |website=youtube |publisher=Netflix |accessdate=2022-02-20}}</ref>

