== 製作 ==
2021年1月21，[[Netflix|Netflix]]官方宣佈續訂第二季，該季會聚焦在安東尼的感情生活。<ref>{{cite news |author1=LAUREN PUCKETT AND HILARY WEAVER |title=Bridgerton Season 2: Everything We Know, From Regé-Jean Page’s Departure To New Cast Members |url=https://www.elle.com/culture/movies-tv/a35083612/bridgerton-season-2-news-release-date-cast-spoilers/ |accessdate=2021-06-10 |work=Elle us |archive-date=2021-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211210162306/https://www.elle.com/culture/movies-tv/a35083612/bridgerton-season-2-news-release-date-cast-spoilers/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>同年2月，曾在《[[性愛自修室|性愛自修室]]》演出的[[席夢·艾希莉|席夢·艾希莉]]加入劇組。2021年4月，[[Netflix|Netflix]]以及{{link-en|Shondaland|Shondaland}} 皆宣布[[雷吉-讓·佩吉|雷吉-讓·佩吉]]不會回歸第二季的製作，而Page本人解釋原因是當初簽訂合約時，他以為此劇只會是個迷你劇集。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2021/tv/news/rege-jean-page-bridgerton-season-2-1234942827/ |website=Variety |accessdate=2021-04-05 |ref=‘Bridgerton’ Breakout Regé-Jean Page Will Not Appear in Season 2 |title=存档副本 |archive-date=2021-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211226203855/https://variety.com/2021/tv/news/rege-jean-page-bridgerton-season-2-1234942827/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，同月13號，官分宣布續訂第三、四季。<ref>{{cite news |author1=JULIE KOSIN |title=Bridgerton Has Been Renewed For Seasons 3 And 4 |url=https://www.elle.com/culture/movies-tv/a36111208/bridgerton-season-3-news-release-date-cast-spoilers/ |accessdate=2021-06-10 |work=Elle us |archive-date=2021-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210610060931/https://www.elle.com/culture/movies-tv/a36111208/bridgerton-season-3-news-release-date-cast-spoilers/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>由於該劇的成功，Netflix宣布製作劇情聚焦於年輕的[[梅克倫堡-施特雷利茨的夏洛特|夏綠蒂王后]]的衍生劇集。<ref>{{cite news |author1=Nellie Andreeva |title=‘Bridgerton’ Gets Young Queen Charlotte Spinoff From Shonda Rhimes, Sets Jess Brownell As Season 3 & 4 Showrunner |url=https://deadline.com/2021/05/bridgerton-young-queen-charlotte-spinoff-prequel-shonda-rhimes-jess-brownell-season-3-4-showrunner-chris-van-dusen-exit-1234756520/ |accessdate=2021-07-05 |work=Deadline |archive-date=2021-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211109082755/https://deadline.com/2021/05/bridgerton-young-queen-charlotte-spinoff-prequel-shonda-rhimes-jess-brownell-season-3-4-showrunner-chris-van-dusen-exit-1234756520/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

